<p>英 /wɜːs/    美 /wɜːrs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>更坏的事</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="for-the-worse">for the worse</h3>
<p>1.<strong>向更坏的方向：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sick man’s condition changed for the worse. 
这位病人的病情恶化了。</p></div></div>